{"tid":2091983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］杜絕藍絲移民英國","createTime":"2020-07-03T03:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T13:13:41.000Z","uid":69533,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b84527e73da1f83abe789f3974e7999b9330d3","tid":2091983,"uid":69533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"相信大家都留意到班藍絲開始諗緊移民去英國，有啲直頭係無錢諗住去做寄生蟲、拎人哋嘅福利。有見及此，為咗避免藍絲攞著數之餘，亦都避免呢啲小粉紅影響香港形象，希望大家一齊完善一下通報機制。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>做開國際線嘅議員/手足 </ins></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-可以搵一個做BNO線代表，統整晒藍絲嘅資料，然後交俾相應嘅英國議員/部門<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>其他手足</ins></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-搜集唔同藍絲嘅資料（尤其喺啲移民group有開聲嘅）<br />\n-將資料交俾上述提到嘅BNO線代表  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家有啲咩睇法？"},{"pid":"e36a37699a058a21d7baa7e57b3e259c68ba3552","tid":2091983,"uid":273703,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"去到外國仲要小心D中國人，好多小粉紅做間諜到時可能會幫中國大使館綁架香港人要脅你，唔好諗住去左就冇事，睇下新疆人去左外地都比人恐嚇要脅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時去到外地都要繼續做情報工作，去 MI5 CIA 舉報，收D中國間諜皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人就係 Chinazi Hunter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全球哨兵，清理小粉紅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去左英國就參軍，海外建軍，建立全面軍事化組織，用三十年四十年都一定要報仇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算拎唔返香港，都要做 Chinazi Hunter，全球性篤灰，起曬D中國人社團出黎，香港高官仔女，幫中國逼害人既公司底，將中共爪牙連根拔起"},{"pid":"e4f2796157f68a00de4c7a8e00a2d121c0336c83","tid":2091983,"uid":273703,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"香港有 200 萬哨兵，完善情報網絡，全球性追撃中共，趕所有中共爪牙返大陸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629aaa57e5d3e37d1143f24d0ef6624ceb95a47b","tid":2091983,"uid":69533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e4f2796157f68a00de4c7a8e00a2d121c0336c83","tid":2091983,"uid":273703,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:38:00.000Z","msg":"香港有 200 萬哨兵，完善情報網絡，全球性追撃中共，趕所有中共爪牙返大陸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:47:24.000Z","msg":"無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中共滲透太嚴重，但首要係舉報咗啲香港藍絲先，唔好俾佢哋有機會拎BNO移民英國。"},{"pid":"a3509fb8ea85911cf3f8e49ea6fe64fc8f9d6ae3","tid":2091983,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:52:38.000Z","msg":"係社交媒體見到親友有藍絲言論即刻cut圖<br />\n當佢地用BNO去英國時為英國安全一定要舉報佢<br />\n如果知道佢地返中國再向大陸舉報佢地第二次<br />\n等佢地兩邊不是人"},{"pid":"0e9749c926beca077b0a28e183baabb8bd3cd225","tid":2091983,"uid":69533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3509fb8ea85911cf3f8e49ea6fe64fc8f9d6ae3","tid":2091983,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:52:38.000Z","msg":"係社交媒體見到親友有藍絲言論即刻cut圖<br />\n當佢地用BNO去英國時為英國安全一定要舉報佢<br />\n如果知道佢地返中國再向大陸舉報佢地第二次<br />\n等佢地兩邊不是人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 齊齊cap藍絲"},{"pid":"3579a746e9dea66b77455b22749c3bfe4e8ef714","tid":2091983,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:15:37.000Z","msg":"Cap screen and send to HM office<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d353853e70dc563e68f8d9f9cff7181f25a203","tid":2091983,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:17:47.000Z","msg":"真心想問巴打們 你地有冇屋企人係藍 但一知道BNO 依家差唔多平權後 即刻扯哂旗咁？"},{"pid":"e34b8417bab8e4d2826beca50f0718dc78cc7f94","tid":2091983,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:19:29.000Z","msg":"查3代, 睇下有冇同某黨有任何聯繫<br />\n例如近親係幹部、高官<br />\n有就ban得"},{"pid":"739fadb4c9abc70bd84a55a1ced841531481ef